<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
  <title>FAQ — WirfonCloud</title>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<section class="page-banner" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0199ef 0%, #005fa3 100%);">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p>Everything you need to know about WirfonCloud training and consulting.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <div class="accordion">
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>What types of training courses does WirfonCloud offer?</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <p>WirfonCloud offers a wide range of training courses in various areas of cloud computing, including AWS fundamentals, Linux fundamentals, networking fundamentals, AWS architecture, and SCRUM. We also provide coaching and mentoring services for individuals starting their cloud journey.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Who can benefit from WirfonCloud's training services?</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <p>Our training services are designed to benefit individuals from all backgrounds, whether they are complete beginners or experienced professionals. We welcome anyone who is eager to learn and build a career in cloud computing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Are the training courses suitable for individuals without a technical background?</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <p>Absolutely! Our courses are designed to cater to individuals with diverse backgrounds. We believe that cloud computing should be accessible to everyone, regardless of their technical expertise. Our trainers provide comprehensive explanations and hands-on exercises to ensure a clear understanding of the concepts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Can I receive a certificate upon completing a training course?</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <p>Yes, upon successful completion of our training courses, you will receive a certificate of completion. Our courses are designed to prepare individuals for industry-recognized certifications, such as AWS certifications, which can further enhance your professional credentials.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
